                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰萤棱锥"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">冰萤</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/1a979041a9881649ba69332b20dd5820_4421361652799067673.png",
                "id": "talent37226",
                "key": "雾虚摇唤",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雾虚摇唤"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成5点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，本角色附着<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">流萤护罩</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/8d60085e1f79ee9a2bb87006d7f2d32c_1352391964926778194.png",
                "id": "talent68639",
                "key": "冰枝白花",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰枝白花"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到3次）</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">愚人众 · 冰萤术士「普通攻击」后：</span>此牌<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">愚人众 · 冰萤术士受到发生元素反应的伤害后：</span>此牌<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>-1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8332858692182745968.png",
                "id": "talent55506",
                "key": "冰萤",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/1467dd7dd3fec80047e77cc996621508_8264366558691582431.png",
                "title": "冰萤"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_3596343439023884151.png",
                "id": "talent66699",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">流萤护罩</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>为我方出战角色提供<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">1点护盾</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">创建时：</span>如果我放场上存在<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">冰萤</span>，则额外提供其<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>。（最多额外提供3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6983108032915946298.png",
